[2] Wei Tang ,Ching-Shan Leu, Lee F.C, “Charge control for zero-voltage-switching multiresonant converter”, Power Electronics, IEEE Transactions on , Volume: 11 , Issue: 2 , March 1996, Pages:270 – 274.
